data.description: Two year rate buy down negotiable. The expansive covered front porch lures you to this large beautiful home with stacked stone and brick water table accents. Charm galore! Open floorplan with split bedrooms, highlighted by expansive gleaming hardwood floors, welcome you into the spacious separate formal dining room and over-sized great room. The high cathedral ceiling and large fireplace makes a dramatic impression. Large kitchen boasts ample storage in tall cabinets, granite counters and breakfast bar. Open view to the spacious breakfast area and great room. Love the large private master suite on the main level which gives great privacy from other bedrooms. Oversized walk-in closet with custom shelving. Private bathroom has a large garden tub, and glass doored separate shower. 2 additional bedrooms on the main level share a full bath in the private hallway. Upstairs features the 4th private ensuite bedroom and full bath. A a perfect space for family or guests seeking their own sanctuary. Plenty of space for entertaining family and friends inside and out on the half acre lot. Rocking chair front porch, expanded patio. Room to add outdoor kitchen, playground, decking, hardscapes, a he/she shed for extra storage or in-law suite, water features will add glam to the large private back yard. Spacious walk-in laundry room with full sized window. Storage galore. Home served by city water and sewer. Easy lawncare enhanced by a water sprinkler system. Leisurely walk to the community pool, playground, and basketball courts. Peaceful community is tucked away, just 3 minutes to the heart of Gray make this a perfect location for elegant and convenient living. Close access to I-75, Macon, Milledegville, Tanger Outlets, too. Make it your home!
